Introduction

M.M.D (better known as the romanization of their korean name, MAMADOL) is a project group formed through 'Mama The Idol', a TVN show about female idols that put their careers on hiatus to become mothers and are trying to debut again. The 6 members showed their skills through the episodes and were able to debut after reaching the goal of 20000 followers on Instagram and 2000 fanclub members.
